premise_source_doc_sentence: Grumpy Old Men is a 1993 American romantic comedy-drama film starring Jack Lemmon , Walter Matthau and Ann-Margret , with Burgess Meredith , Daryl Hannah , Kevin Pollak , Ossie Davis and Buck Henry .

Slaughter on Tenth Avenue is a 1957 American film noir crime film directed by Arnold Laven starring Richard Egan , Jan Sterling , Dan Duryea , Julie Adams , Walter Matthau , Charles McGraw and Sam Levene .
